@page
@model OmerBagrutSite.Pages.HomeModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Welcome!";
}
 
<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/HomeStyle.css" />

<section class="hero">
    <h1>Welcome to My Site</h1>
    <p>Your guide to smart and healthy eating</p>
</section>

<main class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/pic_calories.jpg" alt="Calories" />
        <h2>What Are Calories?</h2>
        <p>Calories are energy units. When you eat or drink, you supply your body with fuel to perform vital functions like breathing, thinking, and exercising. Managing your calorie intake is essential for weight control and health.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/pic_sugar.jpg" alt="Sugar" />
        <h2>Sugar: Friend or Foe?</h2>
        <p>Sugar gives quick energy, but too much may cause weight gain and chronic diseases. Many processed foods hide added sugars — always check nutrition labels.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/pic_macros.jpg" alt="Macros" />
        <h2>Macronutrients</h2>
        <p>Macronutrients are carbs, proteins, and fats. A balanced diet includes all three in the right portions to support your body’s needs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/pic_micros.jpg" alt="Micronutrients" />
        <h2>Micronutrients</h2>
        <p>Vitamins and minerals are needed in smaller amounts but are crucial for immune health, metabolism, and development.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/pic_hydration.jpg" alt="Hydration" />
        <h2>Hydration</h2>
        <p>Water makes up 60% of your body. It helps transport nutrients, regulate temperature, and flush waste. Aim for 6–8 cups per day.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card tip-box">
        <h2>Smart Eating Tips</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>🥗 Eat more whole foods</li>
            <li>💧 Stay hydrated</li>
            <li>🥩 Choose lean proteins</li>
            <li>🍎 Fill half your plate with vegetables</li>
            <li>🚫 Limit processed sugar</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</main>

<footer class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2025 Me | Stay informed. Stay healthy.</p>
</footer>

